  "description": "DBI is a database access Application Programming Interface (API) for the Perl Language. The DBI API Specification defines a set of functions, variables and conventions that provide a consistent database interface independent of the actual database being used.  \n\nSecurity Fix(es):  \n\n  * DBI: DBI: Buffer overflow in error handling can lead to arbitrary code execution (CVE-2026-9698)\n\n\nFor more details about the security issue(s), including the impact, a CVSS score, acknowledgments, and other related information, refer to the CVE page(s) listed in the References section.\n",
